    <h1>Box Design Practice</h1>
    <h2>Box 1</h2>
    <p>This is the first box,It has a light blue background rounded cormers,and a solid border. This box includes
        an image below to enhance the visual appeal of the content. The image should be relevant to the content
        described and help illustrate the point.
    </p>
    <img src="images/box1.jpg" alt="画像１">
    <h2>Box 2</h2>
    <p>This is the second box. It has a light orange background, slightly rounded cormers, a solid border, and a
        shadow. Including an image in this box helps break up the text and provides a visual example of the 
        content. The use of CSS box shadow enhances the 3D effect of this box.
    </p>
